The paper deals with the problem of maximizing secrecy energy efficiency in a mobile relaying system using a UAV. This involves optimizing communication scheduling, power allocation, and UAV trajectory. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper deals with security and eavesdropping, it may also belong to the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-category. Finally, since the paper proposes an algorithm to solve the optimization problem, it may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
